00:25:42.070 --> 00:25:42.080
because

00:25:42.080 --> 00:25:45.269
you heard it.

00:25:45.279 --> 00:25:51.190
You heard it

00:25:51.200 --> 00:25:54.149
when she smiles and she grins from ear

00:25:54.159 --> 00:25:56.630
to ear because she knew the Holy Spirit

00:25:56.640 --> 00:26:00.789
