02:34:59.120 --> 02:35:01.910
Do you get anything out of these things?

02:35:01.920 --> 02:35:03.590
Does it bless you? I pray it does.

02:35:03.600 --> 02:35:05.510
Somebody's getting something out of

02:35:05.520 --> 02:35:08.870
6,100 of you. I pray that somebody gets

02:35:08.880 --> 02:35:12.150
something, gets refreshed, gets in the

02:35:12.160 --> 02:35:13.830
river, and then you jump right back

02:35:13.840 --> 02:35:16.550
in there and you go at it.

02:35:16.560 --> 02:35:18.070
But we're so grateful every single one

02:35:18.080 --> 02:35:21.110
of you are here. But I'll end it there.

02:35:21.120 --> 02:35:23.910
It's good. And we can pray again. I'll

02:35:23.920 --> 02:35:25.110
try to come back tomorrow. I've been

02:35:25.120 --> 02:35:26.630
doing every other day to let the people

02:35:26.640 --> 02:35:27.990
watch the video because there's so many

02:35:28.000 --> 02:35:29.910
of you that it takes you a long time to

02:35:29.920 --> 02:35:32.950
get through two and a half hours, but I

02:35:32.960 --> 02:35:35.190
don't want you to miss nothing.

02:35:35.200 --> 02:35:37.270
And I told Braden, I said, "It seems

02:35:37.280 --> 02:35:39.270
like such a waste to keep jumping in and

02:35:39.280 --> 02:35:41.429
doing video and then know

02:35:41.429 --> 02:35:41.439
that

02:35:41.439 --> 02:35:43.429
nobody watches it. And then you

02:35:43.439 --> 02:35:44.870
get the ones and they get to being

02:35:44.880 --> 02:35:46.550
stragglers and if you give them more

02:35:46.560 --> 02:35:49.110
days they'll watch it all and they're

02:35:49.120 --> 02:35:50.550
getting what the Lord's wanting for them

02:35:50.560 --> 02:35:53.830
to pray through their own prayer life.

02:35:53.840 --> 02:35:55.670
You know,

02:35:55.680 --> 02:35:59.110
I want so badly

02:35:59.120 --> 02:36:01.990
for you to find him in a more intimate

02:36:02.000 --> 02:36:04.389
relationship with him so that

02:36:04.399 --> 02:36:06.710
you go from glory to glory every single

02:36:06.720 --> 02:36:08.870
day and you find him and he's your

02:36:08.880 --> 02:36:11.190
friend,

02:36:11.200 --> 02:36:15.030
he becomes a friend.

02:36:15.040 --> 02:36:16.950
That's what has always been about for me

02:36:16.960 --> 02:36:20.550
is being a friend to Jesus

02:36:20.560 --> 02:36:25.750
that he has somebody to talk to.

02:36:25.760 --> 02:36:28.950
So, we love you all. We pray it blessed

02:36:28.960 --> 02:36:31.190
you. And I don't mean to be critical

02:36:31.200 --> 02:36:32.950
towards people. I want you to always

02:36:32.960 --> 02:36:36.070
know that. My heart is to love on folks,

02:36:36.080 --> 02:36:40.309
but sometimes people provoke me a

02:36:40.319 --> 02:36:43.190
little bit. But God bless everybody.

02:36:43.200 --> 02:36:45.670
Love you. We will see you again soon.

02:36:45.680 --> 02:36:49.030
Remember, put a smile on your face and a

02:36:49.040 --> 02:36:51.590
song in your heart. Jesus loves you so

02:36:51.600 --> 02:36:53.590
much and we love you. God bless you and

02:36:53.600 --> 02:36:57.720
we'll see you again. Bye bye.

